title: Jeff Dunham: Unhinged in Hollywood (2015)

cast.name: Jeff Dunham
cast.character: Himself /              Walter /              Bubba J /              Peanut /              Achmed

overview: Previously unseen stand-up comedy by Jeff Dunham. Sketches include popular characters. Brad Paisley performs too! Special appearances by comic Chris Parnell and former UFC champion Chuck Liddell.
storyline: Jeff Dunham stars in this one-hour special from the world famous Dolby Theatre in Hollywood. The telecast features a live performance by country music superstar Brad Paisley, as well as never before seen stand-up and behind-the-scenes sketches featuring Dunham and his eccentric beloved characters.
